eu.eco2clouds.accounting.monitoringcollector

Class MainLauncher

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.eco2clouds.accounting.monitoringcollector.MainLauncher

  • public class MainLauncher
extends java.lang.Object
    Wrapper class, the application entry point. Contains a main method that instantiates a MonitoringCollector object and starts it. As the start method is asynchronous, the main thread then waits for a key press to shut down.
